CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 24, 1946, pg. 17, reads: "Favorite - Solomon Hughes, Minneapolis wizard of the links will be one of the men to keep an eye on during the forthcoming National Golf Championship Tourney at South Park from Aug. 27 through Aug. 30. Hughes has been a consistent winner in open tournaments throughout the country and held the crown in 1935. - Harris photo."
TitMainTitle: Golfer Solomon Hughes swinging golf club on golf course
